RBI Says Need for Recognition of Interest Rate Risks

-- B y   A n d r e w   M a c a s k i l l
-- 
2011-02-21T15:07:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-21/rbi-says-need-for-recognition-of-interest-rate-risks-correct-.html
(Corrects to say Thimpu is Bhutan’s capital in first
paragraph.)  India’s companies and banks need to
improve their risk management practices by increasing their
recognition of interest rate and currency risks,  Reserve Bank  of  India  Deputy Governor Shyamala Gopinath said at a foreign
exchange dealers conference in Bhutan’s capital Thimpu on Feb.
18.  The Mumbai-based Indian central bank posted the speech on
its website today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Macaskill at 
 amacaskill@bloomberg.net  